title: U.S. Energy Secretary Says Iran Has ‘Big Job’ on Nuclear Deal
text:
It remains unclear how long it will take to implement the nuclear agreement between Iran and six major powers and lift sanctions on Tehran, U.S. Energy Secretary Ernest Moniz said Monday, with Iran still having a “big job” ahead to meet its commitments.
